<blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">There is a serious consideration here about wh=
ether Meta Platforms Inc.=E2=80=99s co-founder, CEO and controlling shareho=
lder has a duty to disclose his MMA [<em>mixed martial arts</em>] activitie=
