it material to a reasonable investor to know what the executives are doing?=
 Is there danger and uniqueness to it? MMA is something that most of us don=
=E2=80=99t do."</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">It=E2=80=99s not that unreasonable to expect Z=
uckerberg will get injured again one day. About three in five MMA fights ha=
d at least one injury, according to an article published in the Orthopaedic=
 Journal of Sports Medicine that reviewed 503 amateur and professional cont=
ests in 2018 and 2019. Zuckerberg=E2=80=99s injury was just during training=
. He tore a ligament in his knee, a joint that one could argue isn=E2=80=99=
t necessary to run a social media company (especially if he=E2=80=99s spend=
ing time in his virtual reality metaverse). But what about his brain? Head =
injuries appear to be higher risk if he doesn=E2=80=99t win his fights; of =
losers=E2=80=99 injuries in the Journal=E2=80=99s review, 17% were concussi=
ons.</p>
</blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Look, nobody is more into =E2=80=9Ceverything =
is securities fraud=E2=80=9D than me, but I can=E2=80=99t=C2=A0<em>really=
=C2=A0</em>imagine Meta getting sued for this if Zuckerberg gets a concussi=
on. Everyone takes lots of risks in life, sometimes accidents happen to CEO=
s, and those accidents=C2=A0<em>probably=C2=A0</em>aren=E2=80=99t actually =
fraud. (Not legal advice!)</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Still, why=C2=A0<em>hasn=E2=80=99t=C2=A0</em>M=
eta added a risk factor for this? Not because it is legally required, I mea=
n, but just because it would be fun for the lawyers? Add a sentence to the =
risk factors like =E2=80=9Cour CEO likes to go to gyms to get punched in th=
e face, and if he gets punched really hard in the wrong part of his face th=
en we may be unable to execute on our product roadmap=E2=80=9D? Surely writ=
ing that sentence is more fun for Meta=E2=80=99s lawyers than whatever else=
 they=E2=80=99ve got going on in their day, even if it is technically less =
important.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">The <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusi=
ness.com/click/33367080.258416/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9vcGluaW9u=
